%p Dear #{@subscription.reader.forename} #{@subscription.reader.surname},

%p Your NZFFA subscription will expire in #{@subscription.days_to_expire} days

- link = renew_subscriptions_url(:reader_id => @subscription.reader_id, :token => @subscription.reader.perishable_token, :host => ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host])
- print_link = print_renewal_subscriptions_url(:reader_id => @subscription.reader_id, :token => @subscription.reader.perishable_token, :host => ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host])
%p To renew your subscription online please visit #{link_to(link, link)}.

%p To print your subscription renewal form please visit #{link_to(print_link, print_link)}.

%p
  Thank you,
  %br
  The NZFFA team.
